casebody.data:
Tuesday, November 29, 1994

MOTION DOCKET

94- 2418. State v. Patrick. Lawrence County, No. 94-CA-02.

This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and a claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution pending appeal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay of execution pending appeal be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective November 23, 1994.
